<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cmn" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>客户管理</title>
<header th:replace="comm :: checkManagerLogin"></header>
<header th:replace="comm :: header_web"></header>
<style type="text/css">
a{text-decoration:underline;}
